    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition, making it a solid choice for someone seeking a reliable daily driver without the high price tag of a newer model. While the engine starts up every time and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, the car does show its age with some visible cosmetic wear on the exterior and minor staining on the interior upholstery. It has been well-maintained mechanically to ensure it remains dependable for commuting. Prospective buyers can expect a functional, honest vehicle that gets the job done reliably.",
